<div class="article-container">
  <h1 class="page-title">关于</h1>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>欢迎访问我的博客！</p>
    <p>我是 boybeak，一名热爱技术的开发者。</p>
    <p>这个博客记录了我的技术分享、生活感悟和读书心得。</p>
    <p>如果你有任何问题或建议，欢迎通过以下方式联系我：</p>
    <div class="contact-links">
      <% if (theme.custom.social_links && theme.custom.social_links.length > 0) { %>
      <% theme.custom.social_links.forEach(function(link) { %>
      <% if (link.url) { %>
      <a href="<%= link.url.indexOf('mailto:') === 0 ? link.url : link.url %>" class="social-link" title="<%= link.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + link.name.slice(1) %>" <%= link.url.indexOf('mailto:') === 0 ? '' : 'target="_blank"' %>>
        <% if (link.icon && (link.icon.indexOf('/') > -1 || link.icon.indexOf('.') > -1)) { %>
        <img src="<%= config.root %><%= link.icon %>" alt="<%= link.name %>" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; object-fit: contain;">
        <% } else { %>
        <span class="material-icons"><%= link.icon %></span>
        <% } %>
        <%= link.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + link.name.slice(1) %>
      </a>
      <% } %>
      <% }); %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-content {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.about-content p {
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.contact-links {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.contact-links .social-link {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  color: var(--text-color);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  background-color: var(--tag-bg);
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  width: auto;
  height: auto;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.contact-links .social-link:hover {
  background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--tag-bg) 80%, black);
}
</style>